{"tid":1800384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB居然加廣告費，洗版無效了？","createTime":"2019-12-27T18:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T23:46:01.000Z","uid":171506,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb32acb50eaee6333600af4dcf29ac73e9af32e","tid":1800384,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191227/60422586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191227%2F60422586&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=bdc4a784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191227%2F60422586&h=42587d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191227/60422586</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【搵舊客笨】TVB鼠年新春廣告價格較2018年貴4.5% 舊客加幅比新客多<br />\n10小時前<br />\n即時財經<br />\n<br />\nTVB近日公佈明年《恭喜發財》賀年廣告套裝。<br />\n<br />\n電視廣播 (511，TVB) 近日公佈明年《恭喜發財》賀年廣告套裝，雖然面對網民號召杯葛，但價格依然「企硬」，甚至比2018年貴。<br />\n<br />\n最近的廣告套裝價格一如以往分為平、中、貴三種，依播放次數而定。最貴的10秒「套裝A」分別在翡翠台、J2及無綫財經‧資訊台播放10秒廣告115次，價格為22.8萬。價格跟今年一樣，但對比2018年同一套裝的21.8萬貴4.5%，而5秒廣告則由10.8萬增至11.18萬，增幅為3.5%。<br />\n<br />\nTVB一如以往都會予預定計劃MU，SU及OC價格保障的客戶（舊客）提供折扣，但折算下舊客加幅更多，如10秒「套裝A」由2018年的19.8萬元增至20.8萬元，增幅達5%；而5秒則由9.8萬元加價至10.38萬元，增幅達5.9%。而記者亦計算套裝B及C加幅，舊客加幅比新客多。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，TVB增設「套裝D」，舊客價最平3,980元播放20次5秒廣告，惟必須最少購買A、B或C套裝其中一份。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，來年農曆新年比今年早，但TVB僅將由公司負責製作的賀年廣告收件截止日期提早一天至1月13日，變相延遲截止日期。"},{"pid":"409aab6f566ce07b5b460fa91179b5fb32dd5700","tid":1800384,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:08:04.000Z","msg":"要輸了...."},{"pid":"7aab060f9c787fd8afd10fdd0ceccf8057ca3db1","tid":1800384,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:08:16.000Z","msg":"請支持2號習近平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800377</a>"},{"pid":"6740822fcfdbb43f3f29858e84fa5c3c88a106c0","tid":1800384,"uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"加到一億播一次都得架<br />\n有冇人比錢咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec9f0e0264a53d3324c95405175a8a8cfbd0b07","tid":1800384,"uid":127067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">［緊急］新德國聯署 唔係上星期個份 仲差3萬人 最後2日</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[第二份德國聯署] Enzo Mazak：得返兩日咋，我唔撚會放棄直至成功。香港人去哂邊？你地都唔好放棄我ok？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duQMB7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduQMB7A.png&h=95a3891d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地推到要放棄啦 香港人爭氣好唔好？ 有哂教學 5分鐘搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1.1 維園見"},{"pid":"b4600788d9a64541e13e250474a46e191a102582","tid":1800384,"uid":39182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁既情況都仲同 TVB 續約，證明個廣告客戶都好需要 TVB, 咁當然加多啲去補返流失咗嘅客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff539064cda5a143c50cf6de27678921ff4ec28","tid":1800384,"uid":135661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"應該會多左好多蝗話廣告"},{"pid":"c398c6265dc2bf3ac19dcafbb09fad2ecde95fb3","tid":1800384,"uid":171506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"有古怪<br />\n<br />\n可能中共搵中資鳩落廣告，保住CCTVB"},{"pid":"332c647b35b6bcbdb3b7cbf81f77db7c3fad2f8f","tid":1800384,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco